text: San José del General is a corregimiento in Omar Torrijos Herrera Special District, Colón Province, Panama with a population of 2,248 as of 2010. Its population as of 1990 was 1,422; its population as of 2000 was 1,207. Until February 20, 2018 this corregimiento was part of Donoso District. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Colón Province
title: San José del General
